Text: My god, this band is such a great, chill, stony band, if i see this album in stores i vow, i will buy it.
This is one awesome album! Download it!
LOOK FOR PHINOT: MY TORRENT OF THE XX HAS EVERYTHING, THE SINGLES, THE BONUS DISC, REMIXES, AND THE LAST EP ISLANDS!
